    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <opener><dateline><placeName ref="pl0001">Downing</placeName> June 22<hi rend="superscript">d</hi> 1775.</dateline>

                <salute>Dear Sir</salute></opener>
                <p>Thanks for two kind Letters. the extract from <bibl type="authorial"><title ref="bi0160">Dalrymple</title></bibl> was most welcome. if you meet any
                    more about <placeName ref="pl0651">Iona</placeName> or any other island I shall
                    be happy to have it.</p>
                <p>Thanks for the care of the box; whose contents will lay me under great
                    obligations to <persName ref="pe0156">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>
                        Low</persName>. I shall write to him on receit. as to his drawings let him
                    know he may command <persName ref="pe0014">my Servant</persName> to do them over
                    again.</p>
                <p>Thanks also to you on account of <persName ref="pe0165">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Tunstall</persName>: Who I dare say will be grateful.</p>
                <closer><salute>adieu very very busy with the press. <lb/>y<hi rend="superscript">rs</hi> sincerely</salute>
                    <signed><persName ref="pe0232">Tho. Pennant</persName></signed></closer>

                <postscript>
                    <p><persName ref="pe0062">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Darell</persName> an
                        old schoolfellow of mine &amp; very worthy friend of mine will give you a
                        Letter from me. Pray shew him y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> city, &amp;c,
                        &amp;c.</p>


                    <p>Pray tell me in y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> next in what year <persName ref="pe1012">Boethius</persName> was born &amp; when he died.</p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p><address>
                        <addrLine>M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Paton</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Custom house</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Edinburgh</addrLine>
                    </address></p>
            </div>
